verseObjects.content: "Worthy is the Lamb who has been slaughtered to receive power, wealth, wisdom, strength, honor, glory, and praise."
"To the one who sits on the throne and to the Lamb be praise, honor, glory, and the power to rule, forever and ever."
+ \ft Some older versions read, \fqa the twenty-four elders fell down and worshiped the one who lives forever and ever \fqa* .
